0 -14 Td
(## 1\) Local Deployment \(Fastest Start\)) Tj
0 -14 Td
(Best for solo founders/operators who want to launch quickly at low cost.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(### Step-by-step) Tj
0 -14 Td
(1. **Prep machine**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Use a stable Windows or Linux machine that stays online during your work hours.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Ensure at least 8 GB RAM and 20+ GB free disk.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(2. **Install prerequisites**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Install Git, Node.js \(LTS\), and Docker \(if required by your workflows\).) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Verify terminal access and admin rights.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(3. **Install OpenClaw**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Install OpenClaw using official docs flow.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Run health/status checks after install.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(4. **Set up workspace**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Create project folder structure \(memory, scripts, docs, backups\).) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Add baseline memory and SOP files.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(5. **Connect channels**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Connect Telegram/WhatsApp/Discord based on client needs.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Validate inbound and outbound messages.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(6. **Configure safety**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Add approval gates for risky actions.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Restrict credentials to least privilege.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(7. **Deploy first automation**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Implement one high-ROI workflow first.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Test with real sample tasks.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(8. **Handoff and backup**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Provide runbook + quick video walkthrough.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Export/backup workspace and memory files.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
