(## 2\) Cloud VPS Deployment \(24/7 Reliability\)) Tj
0 -14 Td
(Best for clients who need always-on uptime.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(### Step-by-step) Tj
0 -14 Td
(1. **Provision VPS**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Choose provider \(Hetzner, DigitalOcean, Linode, AWS Lightsail\).) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Start with Ubuntu 22.04 LTS \(2 vCPU / 4 GB RAM minimum\).) Tj
0 -14 Td
(2. **Harden server**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Create non-root sudo user.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Disable password SSH; enable SSH keys only.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Enable firewall \(UFW\) and fail2ban.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Install security updates.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(3. **Install runtime stack**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Install Git, Node.js LTS, Docker, and OpenClaw dependencies.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Confirm versions and system health.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(4. **Install OpenClaw**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Install in dedicated service directory.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Configure environment variables and secrets securely.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(5. **Run as service**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Set OpenClaw as systemd service for auto-restart.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Validate boot persistence.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(6. **Attach channels + tools**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Connect required messaging channels.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Test each integration end-to-end.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(7. **Set observability**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Enable logs, uptime checks, and alerting.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Track key workflow failures.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(8. **Backups and DR**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Daily backup of workspace/memory/config.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Document restore runbook.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(### Required commands \(Ubuntu VPS\)) Tj
0 -14 Td
(```bash) Tj
0 -14 Td
(sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y) Tj
0 -14 Td
(sudo adduser deploy) Tj
0 -14 Td
(sudo usermod -aG sudo deploy) Tj
0 -14 Td
(sudo apt install -y ufw fail2ban git curl build-essential) Tj
0 -14 Td
(sudo ufw allow OpenSSH) Tj
0 -14 Td
(sudo ufw enable) Tj
0 -14 Td
(sudo systemctl enable --now fail2ban) Tj
0 -14 Td
(```) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(```bash) Tj
0 -14 Td
(curl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_lts.x | sudo -E bash -) Tj
0 -14 Td
(sudo apt install -y nodejs) Tj
0 -14 Td
(node -v && npm -v) Tj
0 -14 Td
(openclaw status) Tj
0 -14 Td
(openclaw gateway status) Tj
0 -14 Td
(```) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
