(## 3\) Hybrid Deployment \(Security + Reliability\)) Tj
0 -14 Td
(Best for sensitive workflows that must keep some data local.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(### Step-by-step) Tj
0 -14 Td
(1. **Split responsibilities**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Cloud VPS handles orchestration and general automations.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Local host handles sensitive data/tools only.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(2. **Design trust boundaries**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Define what can leave local environment and what cannot.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Document data classification \(public/internal/restricted\).) Tj
0 -14 Td
(3. **Deploy cloud node**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Follow VPS deployment steps above.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(4. **Deploy local node**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Install OpenClaw runtime on local machine.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Restrict local node to private-only workflows.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(5. **Secure communications**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Use secure channels and scoped credentials.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Rotate secrets and revoke unused tokens.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(6. **Workflow routing**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Route sensitive tasks to local node.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Route non-sensitive tasks to cloud node.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(7. **Validation tests**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Confirm sensitive data never leaves local scope.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Test failover behavior when one node is offline.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(8. **Operational handoff**) Tj
0 -14 Td
(   - Provide routing rules + escalation SOP.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
