0 -14 Td
(```bash) Tj
0 -14 Td
(openclaw status) Tj
0 -14 Td
(openclaw gateway status) Tj
0 -14 Td
(```) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(```bash) Tj
0 -14 Td
(# Cloud node maintenance) Tj
0 -14 Td
(sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(# Local node maintenance) Tj
0 -14 Td
(sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y) Tj
0 -14 Td
(```) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
